snippet.title: Lords of Magic:  Legends of Urak - Video Game Trailer. PC Windows, 1998.
snippet.description:
Lords Of Magic - Legends of Urak expansion pack  : official video game  trailer.
Developed by Impressions Games
Published by Sierra in 1998 for PC (Windows).
Year :  1998
System : PC (Windows)
This expansion pack upgrades 'Lords of Magic' to 'Lords of Magic Special Edition.'

Video Found in the Sierra's "Holiday Software Sample" (1998 promotional CD).
